import React from 'react';

const AddUser = () => {
  return (
  <Cards>
   <form>
    <label htmlFor='user-name'>
      Username</label>
    <input type='text' id='user-name'> 
    </input>
    <label htmlFor='Age'>
      Age (years old)
    </label>
    <input type='text' id='Age'> 
    </input>
   </form>
  </Cards>
  ) 
}

export default AddUser
